What do you say at a time like this? <br><br>
I wrote some parting comments at the conclusion of the FORUM, another part of this site that changed me in ways for which I can only be thankfull. I repost them here because they continue to express my feelings about the entire site, a truly human experience and phenomena in a world growing increasingly fragmented like a thousand broken mirrors. <br><br>
My words speak of a comet, contemporary when I wrote them, but still very much a valid image as it has not yet been forgotten.<br><br>
